text: IF Vesta is a sports club in the town of Uppsala in Sweden, established on 8 June 1911. The club runs bandy and soccer. It earlier even ran floorball and ice hockey. The men's bandy team played eleven seasons in the Swedish top division. == References == ==Other websites== *Bandy *Soccer Category:1911 establishments in Europe Category:Bandy clubs in Sweden Category:Floorball clubs in Sweden Category:Ice hockey teams in Sweden Category:Swedish football clubs Category:Uppsala Category:1910s establishments in Sweden
